{"tid":2421899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰翻何俊仁舊賬，指他曾提出辭職公投，其後又作罷。","createTime":"2021-02-25T00:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T17:38:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06e39a0e50d655d6115689428c44929ad17221ab","tid":2421899,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:07:47.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰狙擊何俊仁 放生何君堯<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2015.10.28 05:20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TUuRHjli9VJc0R5U3YchnvbQQ-Y=/1416x945/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PGFH7XYNTY2EK3IYXVM7E6C6WA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTUuRHjli9VJc0R5U3YchnvbQQ-Y%3D%2F1416x945%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPGFH7XYNTY2EK3IYXVM7E6C6WA.jpg&h=f6599c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭松泰（右）在論壇上質問何俊仁（左）為何放棄辭職公投。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今屆熱血公民派出鄭松泰到屯門樂翠區，聲稱狙擊泛民和建制候選人，不過鄭在論壇互片時間，花了三分半鐘不斷狙擊何俊仁，只留下不足半分鐘狙擊建制派候選人何君堯，反觀何俊仁在質詢時全程狙擊建制派，沒花半點時間狙擊熱血公民和前黨友阮偉忠。<br />\n鄭松泰昨一開口便要求何俊仁回應，為何有幾次立法會不用開會，他也不前往屯門出席區議會會議。何俊仁回應時批評鄭松泰最近兩個月為了選舉才「落區開咪鬧人」。<br />\n鄭之後續翻何俊仁舊賬，指他曾提出辭職公投，其後又作罷；何俊仁回應指當時只是以辭職公投作佔領退場機制。鄭足足花了三分半鐘狙擊何俊仁，餘下30秒才向何君堯發問。<br />\n其餘兩位候選人張永偉和沈錦添並沒出席論壇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20151028/JUIDKHNIKUNZZZ4Z64JGWFAB74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20151028%2FJUIDKHNIKUNZZZ4Z64JGWFAB74%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Fiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=462b43f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20151028%2FJUIDKHNIKUNZZZ4Z64JGWFAB74%2F&h=247a64a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20151028/JUIDKHNIKUNZZZ4Z64JGWFAB74/</a>"},{"pid":"64dcccbe05d1be9ed15a1d5352b13cfe6668340b","tid":2421899,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:12:17.000Z","msg":"好似支那人咁長期人格分裂，每日都打倒昨天的我，邊個夠你玩呀建制泰"},{"pid":"946fb465d115364842794da81234de9a5f65fc09","tid":2421899,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"64dcccbe05d1be9ed15a1d5352b13cfe6668340b","tid":2421899,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:12:17.000Z","msg":"好似支那人咁長期人格分裂，每日都打倒昨天的我，邊個夠你玩呀建制泰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"本土泰 冇支持「收緊議事規則」<br />\n何俊仁 有支持「收緊議事規則」"},{"pid":"04d2a517768552cd55a3091c956b246c403f3c83","tid":2421899,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946fb465d115364842794da81234de9a5f65fc09","tid":2421899,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"64dcccbe05d1be9ed15a1d5352b13cfe6668340b","tid":2421899,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:12:17.000Z","msg":"好似支那人咁長期人格分裂，每日都打倒昨天的我，邊個夠你玩呀建制泰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"本土泰 冇支持「收緊議事規則」<br />\n何俊仁 有支持「收緊議事規則」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6xEnd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6xEnd8.jpg&h=1ace7928&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ded46a96ac0a0ebdc399968f0160930e012bc33","tid":2421899,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"泰狗下屆會有支聯辦配票"}]}